#Text=Olympic highlights : August 10 , 2008
#Text=Sunday , August 10 , 2008
#Text=August 10 , 2008 is the 2nd major day of the 2008 Olympic games , the below article lists some of the highlights .
#Text=As a lot of the new records were in swimming events , this articles has several sections on swimming races .
#Text=Events
#Text=Men 's 400 metre individual medley
#Text=Swimmer Michael Phelps won the gold medal for the U.S. Team in the 400 individual medley swimming event .
#Text=Phelps clocked in at 4:03.84 managing to break his previous best time of 4:05.25 by almost 2 seconds , and setting a new world record in the event .
#Text=His gold medal is the first gold medal won in the 2008 games .
#Text=Phelps will swim the men 's 4x100m freestyle relay tomorrow in an attempt to win his second gold medal .
#Text=Laszlo Cseh from Hungary came in second and received the silver medal , while Ryan Lochte from the U.S. came in third to win bronze .
#Text=Men 's 100 metre breaststroke
#Text=In the semifinal of the men 's 100 metre breaststroke , the Norwegian Alexander Dale Oen , set a new Olympic record with a time of 59.16 .
#Text=The Japanese Kitajima Kosuke and the Australian Brenton Rickard finished in second and third place respectively , both with times of under one minute .
#Text=Women 's 400 metre individual medley
#Text=In the final of the women 's 400 metre individual medley , the Australian Stephanie Rice , set a new world record with a time of 4:29.45 .
#Text=By doing this she took the gold medal .
#Text=Rice beat the previous world record by over two seconds .
#Text=The Zimbabwean Kirsty Coventry finished in second and won the silver medal .
#Text=Women 's 4 x 100 metre freestyle relay final
#Text=In the final of the women 's 4 x 100 metre freestyle relay , the team from the Netherlands , set a new world record with a time of 4:29.45 .
#Text=By doing this she took the gold medal .
#Text=The team beat the previous world record by over two seconds , with their time of 3:33.76 .
#Text=The American finished in second and won the silver medal , while the Austraian team , which won in 2004 , took the bronze medal .
#Text=Women 's synchronized 3 metre springboard
#Text=The Chinese Guo Jingjing ( 郭晶晶 ) and Wu Minxia ( 吴敏霞 ) received gold medal for a total of 343.50 points .
#Text=" We have prepared really well beforehand .
